                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/17392e44-9537-11e7-b75f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/17392e44-9537-11e7-b75f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_60a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
